editorialNotes.standard: When a much-loved Canadian icon launches an innovative way for us Canucks to get our Timmy’s faster and easier, well, it’s a natural Editors’ Choice. Bonus: all those languages and games are available for free!

Search for communities that line up with your hobbies; filter posts by posting time, hotness and more; and get a breakdown of your own Redditing history to see where you reaped all that sweet, sweet karma.
